    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-07-28T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-07-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="1794"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1794">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 891.001/33.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <persName type="from">Shah</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">President</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Translation]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-07-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 28, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>With high appreciation of the kind wishes Your Excellency sends me on the
                    occasion of my coronation, I wish to thank you sincerely. In taking hold of the
                    reins of government my first duty will be to draw closer the ties of friendship
                    which so happily subsist between the two peoples.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sultan Ahmad Kadjar</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
